lines.text: Say, you lay a hand on me and I'll sock you so hard your shirt'll run up your spine like a window shade.
I protest, Your Honor, this is contrary to all legal procedure. That woman is not in the witness stand!
Don't you point your finger at me, you big palooka. You can't fry Jenny just because my 'anny-fay' ain't parked where you think it should be.
